f_{X+Y}(z)=\begin{cases}\frac z2 & 0\le z\le1\\ \frac12 & 1\le z\le2\\ \frac{(3-z)}{2} & 2\le z\le 3\\ 0 & \text{elsewhere} \end{cases}
